</strong>: when you find excellent games, you can consume stars to continue to evolve. The evolved games will belong to you. If other players replay or like, they will earn stars for you.<br><br><strong>Join the community</strong>: become a member of the creative game console community! Please be sure to try other players' games, and you will definitely get inspiration from them!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2070880/extras/57c69cf582609d63702b67db5b7a2bc7.poster.avif?t=1725909028\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2070880/extras/57c69cf582609d63702b67db5b7a2bc7.webm?t=1725909028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2070880/extras/57c69cf582609d63702b67db5b7a2bc7.mp4?t=1725909028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
